# Sudo Practice Lab

**Commands Learned:**
- whoami
- ls /root
- sudo ls /root
- sudo -l
- sudo mkdir /tmp/test_sudo_lab
- sudo rmdir /tmp/test_sudo_lab
- sudo !!

**Lessons:**
- Normal users cannot access root-only files
- `sudo` allows temporary root privileges
- Always use `sudo` safely; mistakes can affect the system
